%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20To%20Give%20Up%20Wayanad%20Seat%2C%20Keep%20Raebareli%2C%20Announcement%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20move%20that%20has%20been%20speculated%20for%20a%20while%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20going%20to%20give%20up%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20today%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Raebareli%2C%20which%20he%20had%20also%20won%20with%20a%20big%20margin%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0This%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20sister%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20constituency%20in%20Kerala%2C%20buzz%20about%20which%20has%20been%20building%20up%20for%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20piece%20of%20information%20revealed%20by%20the%20sources%20is%20that%20despite%20a%20clamour%20from%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20unlikely%20to%20take%20up%20the%20role%20of%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20would%20have%20enabled%20him%20to%20get%20Cabinet%20rank%20status%2C%20coordinate%20better%20with%20allies%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20helped%20the%20Congress%20project%20a%20strong%20face%20with%20its%20increased%20presence%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20conveyed%20that%20he%20is%20not%20inclined%20to%20take%20up%20the%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20around%205%20pm%20and%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20Wayanad%20constituency%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20there%20because%20today%20is%20the%20last%20day%20for%20it%20to%20be%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretariat.%20The%20call%20on%20the%20pick%20for%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20may%20also%20be%20made%20during%20the%20meeting%20but%20the%20selection%20of%20the%20Wayanad%20candidate%20can%20wait%20as%20the%20bypoll%20will%20be%20held%20within%20six%20months%20of%20Mr%20Gandhi%20giving%20up%20the%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPractical%20Considerations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20just%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20won%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20where%20he%20had%20emerged%20victorious%20in%202019%20despite%20his%20shock%20defeat%20in%20Amethi%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20by%20a%20margin%20of%203.64%20lakh%20votes.%20This%20was%20eclipsed%20by%20his%20performance%20in%20Raebareli%20-%20helped%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20emotional%20appeal%20to%20voters%20that%20she%20was%20handing%20her%20son%20to%20them%20-%20which%20he%20won%20with%20a%20margin%20of%203.9%20lakh%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Raebareli%20seat%20was%20held%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20since%202004%20until%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Cementing%20its%20status%20as%20a%20Gandhi%20family%20bastion%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20also%20represented%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20grandmother%20and%20former%20PM%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Feroze%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20not%20inclined%20to%20give%20up%20Wayanad%2C%20what%20also%20worked%20in%20favour%20of%20Raebareli%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20it's%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20home%20to%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20The%20astounding%20performance%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party-Congress%20alliance%20in%20the%20state%2C%20where%20it%20won%2043%20of%2080%20constituencies%2C%20reducing%20the%20BJP%20from%2062%20to%2033%2C%20also%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20facing%20a%20dilemma%20and%20was%20still%20undecided%20on%20which%20seat%20he%20would%20retain%2C%20hinting%20only%20that%20his%20final%20decision%20would%20make%20people%20from%20both%20constituencies%20happy.%20Kerala%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chief%20K%20Sudhakaran%20had%20almost%20let%20the%20cat%20out%20of%20the%20bag%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20be%20saddened%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20lead%20the%20nation%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20remain%20in%20Wayanad.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20should%20not%20be%20sad.%20Everyone%20should%20understand%20that%20and%20give%20all%20their%20wishes%20and%20support%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718622720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Frc0ees38_rahul-gandhi_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-give-up-wayanad-seat-keep-raebareli-announcement-soon-5908712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20move%20that%20has%20been%20speculated%20for%20a%20while%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20going%20to%20give%20up%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20today%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Raebareli%2C%20which%20he%20had%20also%20won%20with%20a%20big%20margin%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-give-up-wayanad-seat-keep-raebareli-announcement-soon-5908712%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-give-up-wayanad-seat-keep-raebareli-announcement-soon-5908712%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-give-up-wayanad-seat-keep-raebareli-announcement-soon-5908712%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20faces%20scrutiny%20as%20passenger%20finds%20metal%20blade%20in%20his%20meal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718622689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F17%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X40