en%20two%20weeks%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20concluded%2C%20after%20which%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20begun%20preparing%20for%20Assembly%20polls%20later%20this%20year%2C%20naming%20its%20in-charges%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20very%20important%20state%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20party%20has%20picked%20two%20Union%20Ministers.%20Environment%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20has%20been%20appointed%20the%20in-charge%20while%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20will%20be%20the%20co-in-charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Union%20Minister%2C%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20has%20been%20handed%20charge%20of%20Haryana%20and%20he%20will%20be%20assisted%20by%20former%20Tripura%20chief%20minister%20Biplab%20Kumar%20Deb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jharkhand%2C%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20and%20newly%20appointed%20Union%20Agriculture%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20will%20be%20the%20in-charge%20and%20he%20will%20be%20helped%20by%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20go-to%20man%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparations%20for%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20be%20handled%20by%20Union%20Coal%20and%20Mines%20Minister%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20Link%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20all%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20that%20are%20coming%20up%2C%20Maharashtra%20will%20get%20the%20most%20attention%20not%20only%20because%20it%20is%20home%20to%20the%20financial%20capital%20of%20the%20country%20or%20it%20is%20the%20second-largest%20state%20in%20terms%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20but%20also%20since%20the%20BJP%20is%20fighting%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20with%20an%20entirely%20new%20coalition.%20It%20is%20now%20allied%20with%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20and%20is%20facing%20off%20against%20the%20Congress-Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)-NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%2023%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats%20and%20had%20got%2041%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Its%20new%20coalition%20has%20managed%20to%20achieve%20victory%20in%20only%2017%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20getting%20just%20nine.%20The%20Congress%20rose%20from%20one%20seat%20to%20emerging%20as%20the%20single-largest%20party%20in%20the%20state%2C%20clinching%2013%20on%20its%20own%20and%2030%20with%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhupender%20Yadav%20and%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20were%20in%20charge%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20last%20year%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%20-%20winning%20163%20of%20230%20seats%20-%20despite%20being%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20nearly%20uninterrupted%20since%202003.%20The%20party%20was%20said%20to%20be%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%20and%20Mr%20Yadav%20and%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20turning%20things%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20Combinations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20is%20another%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20struggling%20a%20little%20and%20this%20was%20borne%20out%20by%20its%20tally%20being%20halved%20to%20five%20in%20the%20just%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20which%20it%20had%20swept%20the%20last%20time%20around.%20The%20BJP%20replaced%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20with%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20the%20party%20is%20banking%20on%20Mr%20Pradhan%20and%20Mr%20Deb%20to%20return%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20link%20is%20apparent%20in%20Jharkhand%20too%2C%20where%20Mr%20Chouhan%20has%20been%20made%20the%20in-charge.%20Mr%20Sarma%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20troubleshooter%20and%20his%20skills%20may%20come%20in%20handy%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20oust%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20will%20have%20its%20first%20Assembly%20polls%20since%202014%20and%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP%20did%20not%20contest%20this%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20won%20both%20seats%20in%20Jammu%2C%20where%20there%20have%20been%20a%20spate%20of%20terrorist%20attacks%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718619540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fs6um8hi_bhupendra-yadav_625x300_06_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-preps-for-state-elections-2-ministers-to-be-in-charge-of-maharashtra-5908124%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20hasn't%20even%20been%20two%20weeks%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20concluded%2C%20after%20which%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20the%20oath%20of%20office%20for%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20begun%20preparing%20for%20Assembly%20polls%20later%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-preps-for-state-elections-2-ministers-to-be-in-charge-of-maharashtra-5908124%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-preps-for-state-elections-2-ministers-to-be-in-charge-of-maharashtra-5908124%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-preps-for-state-elections-2-ministers-to-be-in-charge-of-maharashtra-5908124%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Outages%2C%20low%20voltage%2C%20fires%3A%20Delhi%20fights%20power%20woes%20with%20trippy%20ACs%2C%20water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718619349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F05%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1717576812-3842.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Foutages-low-voltage-fires-delhi-fights-power-woes-with-trippy-acs-water-124061700470_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%2C%20by%20June%2012%2C%20the%20national%20capital%20has%20reported%20over%20339%20cases%20of%20fires%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Foutages-low-voltage-fires-delhi-fights-power-woes-with-trippy-acs-water-124061700470_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Foutages-low-voltage-fires-delhi-fights-power-woes-with-trippy-acs-water-124061700470_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Foutages-low-voltage-fires-delhi-fights-power-woes-with-trippy-acs-water-124061700470_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Kavach%3F%20Safety%20System%20Missing%20On%20Bengal%20Route%20Where%20Trains%20Crashed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKavach%2C%20the%20made-in-India%20system%20to%20help%20prevent%20accidents%20if%20two%20trains%20are%20travelling%20on%20the%20same%20line%2C%20was%20not%20available%20on%20the%20tracks%20in%20Darjeeling%20where%20the%20two%20trains%20collided%20today.%20At%20least%20nine%20passengers%20have%20died%20and%20over%2050%20others%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20goods%20train%20rammed%20the%20Kolkata-bound%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20from%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20explaining%20the%20Kavach%20system%20went%20viral%20following%20today's%20crash%2C%20officials%20said%20the%20system%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20installed%20in%20much%20of%20the%20rail%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%20The%20Railways%20plans%20to%20deploy%20the%20safety%20system%20on%20the%20Delhi-Guwahati%20route%20under%20its%20goal%20to%20cover%20over%206%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks%20by%20next%20year.%20Bengal%20falls%20within%20the%203%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks%20set%20to%20be%20protected%20by%20Kavach%20this%20year.%20The%20system%20will%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20Delhi-Howrah%20route%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaya%20Varma%20Sinha%2C%20Chairman%20of%20Railway%20Board%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Kavach%20is%20in%20place%20on%20over%201%2C500%20km%20of%20tracks.%20The%20Centre%20had%20planned%20to%20bring%202%2C000%20km%20of%20rail%20network%20under%20Kavach%20during%202022-23%20and%20aims%20to%20cover%20around%2034%2C000%20km%20of%20rail%20network.%20The%20Indian%20Railway%20system%20is%20over%201%20lakh%20kilometres%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Kavach%20was%20deployed%2C%20something%20like%20this%20accident%20could%20likely%20be%20avoided.%20However%2C%20it's%20a%20costly%20system%20to%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Railway%20Board%20Prempal%20Sharma%20told%20NDTV.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Is%20Kavach%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%20is%20an%20automatic%20train%20protection%20(ATP)%20system%2C%20indigenously-developed%20by%20the%20Research%20Design%20and%20Standards%20Organisation%20(RSCO)%20with%20three%20Indian%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20system%20controls%20the%20speeding%20of%20trains%20but%20also%20helps%20locomotive%20drivers%20to%20avoid%20missing%20danger%20signals%20and%20ensure%20that%20trains%20run%20safely%20especially%20in%20low-visibility%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%20controls%20train%20speed%20by%20automatically%20braking%20if%20the%20driver%20fails%20to%20apply%20the%20brakes%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERFID%20(Radio%20Frequency%20Identification)%20tags%20are%20placed%20on%20tracks%20and%20at%20station%20yard%20and%20signals%20for%20identifying%20the%20tracks%20and%20locating%20the%20train%20and%20its%20direction.%20When%20the%20system%20is%20activated%2C%20all%20trains%20within%205%20km%20will%20stop%20to%20let%20the%20train%20on%20an%20adjacent%20track%20to%20pass%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Board%20Display%20of%20Signal%20Aspect%20(OBDSA)%20helps%20the%20loco%20pilots%20view%20the%20signals%20even%20when%20the%20visibility%20is%20low%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%20Usually%2C%20loco%20pilots%20have%20to%20look%20out%20of%20the%20window%20to%20spot%20the%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20safety%20system%20sends%20a%20signal%20to%20a%20loco%20pilot%20when%20approaching%20a%20'red%20signal'%20and%20applies%20automatic%20brakes%20if%20necessary%20to%20prevent%20overshooting%20the%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said%20he%20had%20personally%20tested%20the%20safety%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRear-end%20collision%20testing%20is%20successful.%20Kavach%20automatically%20stopped%20the%20locomotive%20before%20380%20m%20of%20other%20locomotive%20at%20the%20front%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EHere%20is%20a%20video%20of%20the%20Railways%20Minister%20explaining%20how%20the%20system%20works%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShri%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshwiniVaishnaw%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AshwiniVaishnaw%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnHon'ble%20Railway%20Minister%20briefs%20during%20live%20testing%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fkavach%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%