C%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20registered%20most%20of%20its%20seat%20losses%2C%20its%20drop%20in%20votes%20was%20at%20least%20five%20percentage%20points.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20Kerala%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-results-tamil-nadu-india-bloc-scripts-clean-sweep-in-tamil-nadu-bjp-and-aiadmk-suffer-rout-5815886%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20saw%20a%20rise%20in%20its%20vote%20shares%2C%20though%20this%20climb%20couldn't%20compensate%20for%20the%20losses%20suffered%20elsewhere.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20key%20reasons%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20touch%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20BJP's%20Presidential%20Style%20Election%20Didn't%20Help%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20last%20two%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20sought%20votes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20this%20time%20as%20well%2C%20with%20slogans%20like%20%26quot%3BModi%20ka%20Bharosa%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BModi%20ki%20Guarantee%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BPhir%20ek%20baar%20Modi%20Sarkar%26quot%3B%20becoming%20its%20clarion%20calls.%20However%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20national%20narrative%20and%20the%20interplay%20of%20local%20factors%20in%20various%20states%20queered%20the%20party's%20pitch.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20voting%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20name%20of%20PM%20Modi%20declined%20from%2017%25%20in%202019%20to%2010%25%20this%20time%2C%20according%20to%20post-poll%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20(CSDS).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20voting%20in%20the%20name%20of%20local%20candidates%20rose%20from%2031%25%20to%2036%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Rahul%20Closes%20Leadership%20Gap%20With%20Modi%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20as%20many%20as%2047%25%20of%20respondents%20wanted%20to%20see%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20while%20only%2023%25%20favoured%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20This%20year%2C%20Modi's%20rating%20in%20that%20regard%20dropped%20to%2041%25%2C%20while%20Rahul's%20improved%20to%2027%25.%20Modi's%20lead%20thus%20narrowed%20to%2014%20percentage%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-prime-ministers-have-fared-in-their-home-constituencies-5894958%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20How%20Prime%20Ministers%20Have%20Fared%20in%20Their%20Home%20Constituencies%20In%20Past%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20improvement%20in%20Rahul's%20scores%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20his%20two%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatras%2C%20where%20he%20mingled%20with%20voters%20covering%20thousands%20of%20kilometres.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20decline%20in%20Modi's%20ratings%20could%20be%20due%20to%20fatigue%2C%20overexposure%2C%20as%20well%20as%20natural%20anti-incumbency%20after%20a%2010-year%20tenure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Modi%20Premium%20Reverts%20To%202014%20Levels%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%20BJP%20voters%20in%20the%20CSDS%20post-poll%20survey%20said%20they%20would%20not%20have%20voted%20for%20the%20party%20had%20Modi%20not%20been%20its%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Considering%20that%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20that%20year%20was%2037%25%2C%20it%20can%20be%20construed%20that%20the%20Modi%20factor%20alone%20accounted%20for%20about%2012%25%20of%20the%20party's%20votes.%20In%202024%2C%20this%20premium%20declined%20to%20one-fourth%2C%20reverting%20to%202014%20levels.%20So%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%20received%20a%20similar%20vote%20share%20this%20year%2C%20only%20about%209%25%20of%20the%20votes%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20Modi%20factor%2C%20a%20decline%20of%20three%20percentage%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Congress%20Forged%20Stronger%20Alliances%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20formed%20strategic%20alliances%20in%20many%20states%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20alliances%20made%20in%202019%2C%20mainly%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Newer%20friendships%20comprised%20alliances%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Goa%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20Chandigarh%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party%20(RLP)%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP)%20and%20Left%20parties%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Conference%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-many-maidaan-moments-of-the-2024-lok-sabha-verdict-5858104%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Opinion%3A%20Let's%20Savour%20The%C2%A0%3Ci%3EMaidaan%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0Moments%20Of%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20205%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20stronger%20alliances%20compared%20to%202019.%20Back%20then%2C%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20could%20win%20just%2017%20of%20these%20seats.%20In%20contrast%2C%20this%20year%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20managed%20to%20bag%2094%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20a%20gain%20of%2077.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20won%20157%20of%20these%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20had%20to%20contend%20with%20a%20truncated%20tally%20of%2092%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Ticket%20Discontent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20replaced%20132%20of%20its%20303%20MPs%20who%20had%20won%20in%202019%20-%20a%20replacement%20ratio%20of%2043%25.%20The%20MPs%20replaced%20had%20a%20better%20strike%20rate%20of%2072%25%20against%20the%2066%25%20rate%20for%20the%20MPs%20retained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20turncoats%20were%20a%20bigger%20factor%3B%20of%20the%20441%20seats%20the%20BJP%20vied%20for%2C%20110%20were%20contested%20by%20turncoat%20candidates.%20Of%20them%2C%20only%2041%20could%20win%2C%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%2037%25.%20That's%20almost%20half%20the%20strike%20rate%20of%20the%20MPs%20replaced.%20The%20BJP%20organisation%20clearly%20didn't%20wholeheartedly%20support%20these%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20BJP%20dropped%20only%2026%25%20of%20its%20candidates%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20turned%20the%20elections%20local%20and%20diluted%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20and%20the%20Modi-Yogi%20factors.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20dropped%2015%20of%20its%20MPs%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Here%20as%20well%2C%20it%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20complications%20and%20heartburn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%2C%20coupled%20with%20Opposition-driven%20fears%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20change%20the%20Constitution%20and%20end%20reservations%2C%20damaged%20the%20party's%20prospects%20in%20156%20seats%20where%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20population%20is%20significant.%20Here%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20gained%2053%20seats%2C%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20lost%2034%2C%20and%20others%2019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718613180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F0dh4nq9o_modi-shah-nadda_625x300_06_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frahuls-rise-ticket-troubles-5-reasons-bjp-missed-the-majority-mark-5907435%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20registered%20m