ps%3A%2F%2Fdfs.delhi.gov.in%2Fdfs%2Ffire-safety-precautions-against-electricity-0%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFuses%2520and%2520switches%2520should%2520be%2Cthe%2520plug%2520from%2520the%2520socket.%C2%A0%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Delhi%20Fire%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20approximately%2060%25%20of%20fires%20are%20caused%20by%20electrical%20causes%20such%20as%20short%20circuits%2C%20overheating%2C%20overloading%2C%20and%20improper%20use%20of%20appliances.%20These%20incidents%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20consequences%20if%20proper%20precautions%20are%20not%20followed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20important%20do's%20and%20don'ts%20to%20minimize%20the%20risk%20of%20electrical%20fires%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo's%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20ISI-certified%20appliances%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMake%20sure%20your%20appliances%20meet%20safety%20standards%20to%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20malfunctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20good%20quality%20fuses%20and%20circuit%20breakers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInstall%20correct-rated%20fuses%2C%20miniature%20circuit%20breakers%2C%20and%20earth%20leakage%20circuit%20breakers%20for%20protection%20against%20electrical%20faults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20one%20socket%20per%20appliance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Do%20not%20plug%20too%20many%20appliances%20into%20a%20single%20outlet%20as%20this%20can%20overload%20the%20circuit%20and%20potentially%20cause%20a%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESwitch%20off%20the%20power%20supply%20to%20affected%20areas%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Immediately%20cut%20off%20electricity%20to%20the%20area%20experiencing%20a%20fire%2