idi%20said%20that%20Babar%20should've%20supported%20Shaheen%20and%20declined%20PCB's%20offer%20to%20captain%20the%20team%20at%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20star%20batter%20could've%20earned%20respect%20had%20he%20done%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20decision%20on%20Shaheen's%20captaincy%20had%20been%20made%20and%20you%20%5BPCB%5D%20had%20stated%20that%20he%20will%20remain%20the%20captain%20till%20the%20%5BT20%5D%20World%20Cup%2C%20then%20I%20think%20Babar%20%5BAzam%5D%20should%20have%20supported%20Shaheen%20there%20and%20should%20have%20said%20that%20'no%2C%20if%20you%20have%20made%20him%20%5BShaheen%5D%20the%20captain%2C%20then%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20play%20under%20his%20captaincy%20because%20Shaheen%20has%20been%20playing%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20If%20he%20is%20made%20captain%20and%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20made%20him%20the%20captain%2C%20then%20yes%20I%20will%20support%20him%20and%20play%20under%20his%20captaincy'.%20This%20is%20the%20stance%20Babar%20should've%20taken.%20Babar's%20respect%20would've%20increased%20greatly%20that%20he%20has%20set%20an%20example%20with%20a%20remarkable%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Afridi%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fwz9HfnkRG-0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Broken%20Hearts%20%7C%20The%20Legacy%20of%20Supporting%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20%7C%20Shahid%20Afridi%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfridi%20also%20recalled%20how%20some%20of%20the%20selectors%20themselves%20had%20questioned%20his%20captaincy%20abilities%20after%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20labelling%20Babar%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpathetic%26quot%3B%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20this%20was%20not%20entirely%20the%20fault%20of%20Babar%20because%20some%20of%2