%2Farticleshow%2F111049907.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fharry-regrets-missing-kings-birthday-event-meghan-remains-indifferent-royal-expert%2Famp_articleshow%2F111049907.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fharry-regrets-missing-kings-birthday-event-meghan-remains-indifferent-royal-expert%2Famp_articleshow%2F111049907.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amul%20Seeks%20Return%20Of%20Ice%20Cream%20Tub%20After%20Customer%20Finds%20Centipede%20In%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmul%20on%20Monday%20requested%20a%20woman%20customer%20in%20Noida%20to%20return%20the%20ice%20cream%20tub%2C%20in%20which%20she%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20centipede%2C%20for%20further%20investigation%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20offers%20superior%20quality%20dairy%20products%20in%20both%20India%20and%20global%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20Noida%20has%20claimed%20she%20has%20found%20a%20centipede%20inside%20an%20ice%20cream%20tub%20she%20ordered%20through%20an%20instant%20delivery%20app%2C%20said%20food%20safety%20officials%2C%20who%20have%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20June%2015%2C%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20identified%20herself%20as%20Deepa%20Devi%2C%20shared%20a%20picture%20showing%20the%20insect%20inside%20the%20ice%20cream%20tub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Cooperative%20Milk%20Marketing%20Federation%20(GCMMF)%2C%20which%20markets%20dairy%20products%20under%20Amul%20brand%2C%20regretted%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20the%20woman%20customer%20in%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoida's%20food%20safety%20department%20has%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Amul%20said%20it%20immediately%20responded%20to%20the%20complaint%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20deeply%20regret%20the%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20her%20because%20of%20this%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmul%20said%20its%20team%20was%20trying%20to%20contact%20the%20customer%20continuously%20and%20was%20allowed%20to%20meet%20after%209%3A30%20pm%20on%20the%20same%20day%20(June%2015).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20our%20meeting%20with%20the%20customer%2C%20we%20had%20requested%20the%20customer%20to%20provide%20the%20said%20ice%20cream%20tub%20for%20investigation%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20customer%20refused%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20the%20complaint%20pack%20is%20retrieved%20from%20the%20customer%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20and%20hence%20comment%20specifically%20on%20the%20issue%20which%20involves%20pack%20and%20supply%20chain%20integrity%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Amul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interaction%2C%20the%20customer%20was%20informed%20and%20assured%20about%20Amul's%20state-of-the-art%20ISO-certified%20plants%20which%20are%20automated%20and%20pass%20through%20numerous%20stringent%20quality%20checks%20before%20offering%20any%20product%20for%20sale%20to%20the%20esteemed%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmul%20also%20invited%20the%20customer%20to%20visit%20its%20plant%20to%20assure%20her%20about%20the%20quality%20processes%20being%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmul%20assured%20customers%20about%20the%20superior%20quality%20of%20Amul%20Ice%20Cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmul%20highlighted%20that%20it%20is%20among%20India's%20most%20trusted%20brands%2C%20owned%20by%2036%20lakh%20farmers.%20It%20markets%2022%20billion%20packs%20of%20Amul%20products%20annually%20across%2050%20countries%20with%20the%20highest%20quality%20and%20food%20safety%20standards%20from%20100%20dairies%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20to%20assure%20you%20that%20we%20take%20the%20utmost%20care%20to%20ensure%20our%20products%20are%20safe%2C%20healthy%20and%20nutritious%20to%20serve%20our%20customers%20daily%2C%26quot%3B%20Amul%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cooperative%20organisation%20requested%20the%20customer%20to%20return%20the%20ice%20cream%20tub%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20receive%20the%20complaint%20pack%20from%20the%20customer%2C%20we%20shall%20investigate%20the%20matter%20from%20all%20angles%20and%20again%20get%20back%20to%20our%20customers%20with%20the%20findings%2C%26quot%3B%20Amul%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718602680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fg29ho4o8_centipede-_625x300_16_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famul-seeks-return-of-ice-cream-tub-after-customer-finds-centipede-in-it-5906924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amul%20on%20Monday%20requested%20a%20woman%20customer%20in%20Noida%20to%20return%20the%20ice%20cream%20tub%2C%20in%20which%20she%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20centipede%2C%20for%20further%20investigation%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20offers%20superior%20quality%20dairy%20products%20in%20both%20India%20and%20global%20markets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famul-seeks-return-of-ice-cream-tub-after-customer-finds-centipede-in-it-5906924%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famul-seeks-return-of-ice-cream-tub-after-customer-finds-centipede-in-it-5906924%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famul-seeks-return-of-ice-cream-tub-after-customer-finds-centipede-in-it-5906924%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20taunts%