t%E2%80%99s%20next%20move%20in%20the%20ring%2C%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20alone%20sometimes%20at%20tournaments%20and%20not%20having%20anyone%20to%20look%20at%20in%20the%20stands%2C%20the%20desire%20to%20prove%20people%20who%20said%20%E2%80%98You%E2%80%99re%20fat%2C%20you%20cannot%20do%20anything%20in%20life%E2%80%99%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20hopeful%20that%20her%20story%20will%20be%20a%20beacon%20for%20people%20to%20believe%20in%20themselves%20and%20follow%20their%20calling.%20And%20behind%20Hetal%20stands%20a%20proud%20father%20who%20never%20for%20once%20doubted%20that%20his%20daughter%20would%20achieve%20these%20feats%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMhari%20chori%20chore%20se%20kam%20hai%20ke%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20all%20those%20who%20questioned%20how%20Hetal%E2%80%99s%20simple%20diet%20would%20let%20her%20achieve%20greatness%20in%20sports%2C%20her%20father%20has%20an%20answer%20ready%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EEk%20marwari%20ne%20daal%20bhat%20kha%20ke%20history%20bana%20li%3C%2Fem%3E%20(A%20%3Cem%3EMarwari%3C%2Fem%3E%20girl%20has%20created%20history%20despite%20a%20simple%20vegetarian%20diet).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718377969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fhetal-dave-1718375371.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353156%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22People%20often%20celebrate%20the%20accolades%20and%20glory%20that%20sumo%20wrestler%20Hetal%20Dave%20brought%20to%20India.%20Today%20we%20take%20a%20moment%20to%20celebrate%20the%20man%20who%20made%20it%20possible%2C%20Hetal's%20'papa'%20who%20became%20a%20coach%20so%20his%20daughter%20could%20live%20her%20dream.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamo