%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBut%20why%20do%20these%20facilities%20fail%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mansi%2C%20most%20of%20these%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20in%20the%20long%20run%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20including%20biological%20disturbance%2C%20equipment%20failure%20like%20burnt%20pumps%2C%20or%20the%20choking%20of%20membrane%20filters%20that%20act%20as%20a%20barrier%20to%20separate%20contaminants%20from%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20a%20way%20for%20these%20plants%20to%20anticipate%20these%20problems%20and%20fix%20them%20in%20advance%20to%20improve%20their%20efficiency%20and%20longevity%3F%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fstartup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20are%20developing%20technological%20solutions%20for%20wastewater%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20about%2090%2C000%20installed%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants.%20But%20today%2095%25%20of%20the%20market%20is%20managed%20entirely%20manually%20by%20deploying%20operators%20in%20each%20plant.%20This%20has%20several%20drawbacks%3B%20problems%20are%20detected%20about%20three%20weeks%20late%20after%20breakdowns%20and%20operators%20lack%20the%20expertise%20to%20tackle%20problems.%20Other%20technologies%20in%20the%20market%20only%20make%20dents%20in%20part%20of%20the%20problem%3B%20they%20only%20monitor%20data%20or%20automate%20the%20key%20equipment%20like%20pumps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20brainstorming%20to%20understand%20how%20they%20can%20solve%20this%20problem%20in%20a%20scalable%20manner%2C%20they%20started%20Digital%20Paani%20in%20end%202020%2C%20piloted%20an%20IoT-enabled%20software%20that%20manages%20end-to-end%20operations%20of%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%2C%20and%20saw%20%E2%80%9Cincredible%20results%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20helping%20buildings%20and%20industries%20move%20towards%20water%20neutrality%20and%20reduce%20water%20losses%20across%20their%20campus.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20in%20a%20stepwise%20manner%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Maximise%20recycling%20by%20ensuring%20wastewater%20infrastructure%20is%20working%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Helping%20industries%20and%20residential%20societies%20do%20water%20accounting%20real-time%2C%20know%20where%20they%20are%20having%20water%20losses%2C%20and%20provide%20roadmaps%20to%20reduce%20those%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Actually%20reducing%20those%20losses%20by%20providing%20operational%20excellence%20and%20management%20through%20technology%20for%20key%20assets%20contributing%20to%20water%20losses%20such%20as%20cooling%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20is%20a%20water%20management%20platform%20that%20tracks%20and%20manages%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20performs%20tasks%20like%20equipment%20automation%2C%20providing%20WhatsApp%20updates%20to%20users%2C%20and%20guiding%20process%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20real-time%20insights%2C%20complete%20control%2C%20and%2024%2F7%20management%20with%20actionable%20recommendations%2C%20they%20drive%20operational%20excellence%20for%20sustainable%20water%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mansi%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20our%20platform%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20water%20infrastructure%2C%20telling%20buildings%20what%E2%80%99s%20wrong%20with%20their%20infrastructure%20and%20what%20it%20needs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20providing%20the%20medicine%20to%20fix%20it%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20directing%20technicians%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344518%2Ffind-missing-children-raju-nepali-duars-express-mail-ngo-rescues-trafficked-children-counselling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhatsApp%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20chemical%20dosage%20required%2C%20automating%20equipment%20to%20function%20properly%20or%20directing%20operators%20on%20the%20best%20next%20steps.%20Through%20our%20work%2C%20we%20help%20clients%20save%20crores%20in%20fines%2C%20but%20more%20importantly%2C%20they%20recycle%20their%20wastewater%20%E2%80%94%2090%20million%20litres%20of%20wastewater%20is%20treated%20daily%20at%20plants%20associated%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20over%2040%20industry%20giants%2C%20including%20Tata%20Power%2C%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20Britannia%2C%20and%20Leela%20Hotels%2C%20are%20using%20the%20Gurugram-based%20startup%E2%80%99s%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20do%20you%20treat%20water%20Digital%20Paani%20style%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-300x262.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-500x437.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-768x671.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSnapinsta.app_434552169_933189761637726_8367049811662365564_n_1080-1718112498-150x131.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352678%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20elements%20that%20Digital%20Paani%20works%20with%20to%20address%20their%20water%20treatment%20needs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnlocking%20business%20and%20product%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20log%20in%20design%20inputs%20about%20the%20infrastructure%20into%20our%20software%2C%20we%20create%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20for%20operating%20the%20plant%20in%20real-time.%20Our%20client%20can%20visualise%20the%20asset%20(wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%20and%20can%20gauge%20its%20analytics%20from%20how%20much%20wastewater%20is%20getting%20treated%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20treatment%20being%20achieved%20and%20whether%20the%20equipment%20is%20functioning%20properly%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mansi%20during%20an%20episode%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH3moOD09wNk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20client%20has%20a%20complete%20online%20software%20before%20them%20to%20visualise%20their%20asset.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20inside%20the%20plant%2C%20our%20software%20can%20assess%20and%20interpret%20data%20using%20AI%20to%20detect%20it.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20that%20clients%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20be%20on%20our%20software%20to%20manage%20these%20issues.%20Management%20actions%20are%20happening%20automatically%2C%20whether%20through%20equipment%20control%20or%20by%20telling%20operators%20directly%20what%20to%20do.%20Clients%20just%20receive%20alert%20notifications%20on%20their%20WhatsApp%20number%20to%20make%20things%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20product%20innovation%2C%20Mansi%20argues%2C%20also%20allows%20them%20to%20unlock%20business%20model%20innovation.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20becoming%20an%20add-on%20cost%20for%20facilities%20like%20our%20competitors%2C%20we%20can%20de-risk%20adoption%20and%20offer%20guaranteed%20savings%20through%20two%20models%20which%20no%20one%20else%20in%20the%20market%20can%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mansi%2C%20speaking%20to%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20we%20enable%20plant%20owners%20to%20manage%20plants%20using%20their%20under-utilised%20staff%20like%20electricians%20with%20our%20system%20and%20team%E2%80%99s%20remote%20management%20rather%20than%20outsourcing%20operations%20for%20lack%20of%20expertise.%20This%20allows%20them%20to%20save%20up%20to%2066%25%20of%20operating%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20as%20Rajesh%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20the%20entire%20operations%20contract%20of%20a%20facility%20and%20allow%20service%20provider%20partners%20that%20provide%20physical%20services%20like%20operators%20onsite%20to%20manage%20clusters%20of%20plants%20as%20a%20fleet%20with%20a%20small%20common%20workforce%20rather%20than%20individual%20deployments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20Digital%20Paani%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20%E2%80%9Cintegrates%20every%20aspect%20of%20wastewater%20treatment%20operations%20and%20scales%20the%20expertise%20needed%20to%20handle%20facilities%E2%80%9D%20in%20three%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20First%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98knows%E2%80%99%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20plants%20by%20determining%20how%20each%20facility%20should%20operate%20given%20its%20unique%20physical%20configuration%20and%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20this%20by%20doing%20a%20design%20assessment%20of%20each%20facility%20on%20our%20software%20as%20well%20as%20capturing%20operations%20information%20from%20each%20unit%20operation%20in%20a%20facility.%20This%20data%20spans%20a%20wide%20range%2C%20from%20using%20computer%20vision%20to%20look%20at%20biological%20process%20health%2C%20to%20looking%20at%20electrical%20data%2C%20energy%20data%2C%20pressure%2C%20vibration%2C%20flow%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mansi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Second%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98tells%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20to%20the%20relevant%20stakeholders%20by%20offering%20complete%20visibility%20through%20WhatsApp%20and%20live%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Finally%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98solves%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20by%20executing%20the%20required%20actions%20directly%20through%20automated%20workflows%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20training%20onsite%20teams%2C%20guiding%20their%20daily%20workflow%20and%20validating%20their%20work%20or%20managing%20the%20physical%20operation%20of%20equipment%20through%20our%20in-platform%20automation%20manager.%20When%20things%20start%20going%20wrong%2C%20it%20uses%20data%20streams%20from%20onsite%20sensors%20and%20electrical%20panels%20to%20diagnose%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20drive%20issue%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20recommend%20operational%20and%20physical%20improvements.%20This%20approach%20has%20transformed%20defunct%20facilities%20while%20reducing%20their%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2066%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Here's%20how%20you%20can%20do%20water%20treatment%20with%20Digital%20Paani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDigital%20Paani%20looks%20to%20understand%20the%20physical%20water%20treatment%20infrastructure%20and%20develops%20unique%20tools%20to%20manage%20it.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20industry%20giants%20use%20Digital%20Paani%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansi%20argues%20that%20every%20building%20and%20factory%20can%20rely%20on%20local%20and%20renewable%20wastewater%20for%20up%20to%2090%25%20of%20their%20water%20needs%2C%20a%20vital%20response%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346640%2Fbengaluru-water-scarcity-crisis-solutions-lake-revival-open-wells-rainwater-harvesting-treated-wastewater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20water%20scarcity%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20climate%20change.%20Unfortunately%2C%20as%20she%20stated%20earlier%20in%20this%20article%2C%20about%2075%25%20of%20treatment%20facilities%20end%20up%20dysfunctional%20because%20operations%20are%20manual%20and%20reactive%2C%20and%20the%20expertise%20and%20skills%20needed%20to%20manage%20such%20complex%20operations%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20solving%20the%20above%20issue%20by%20reimagining%20this%20industry%20through%20Digital%20Paani%2C%20which%20effectively%20scales%20the%20needed%20technical%20expertise%20to%20drive%20operational%20excellence%20in%20facilities.%20This%20results%20in%20the%20transformation%20of%20non%20or%20low-functioning%20plants%20to%20high-quality%2C%20compliant%20units%20treating%20100%25%20of%20water%20to%20high-water-quality%20standards%2C%20all%20while%20reducing%20operating%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2030%25.%20Many%20of%20our%20customers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20breakdowns%20significantly%20(up%20to%2085%25)%20and%20reduce%20energy%20consumption%20in%20the%20range%20of%2020%20to%2035%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20importantly%2C%20they%20can%20now%20confidently%20reuse%20this%20water%3B%20many%20of%20our%20customers%20have%20gone%20from%20reusing%2045%25%20of%20their%20water%20on%20average%20to%20around%2080%25.%20This%20is%20why%20major%20players%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20adopting%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20as%20Mansi%20notes%2C%20the%20ease%20of%20integrating%20Digital%20Paani%2C%20which%20functions%20on%20a%20plug-and-play%20model%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20enhances%20its%20appeal%E2%80%9D.%20Treatment%20facilities%20of%20any%20size%20and%20type%20can%20be%20installed%20in%20three%20straightforward%20steps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Site%20survey%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20%5BParallel%5D%20Any%20IoT%20deployment%20needed%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20%5BParallel%5D%20Plant%20onboarding%20onto%20our%20software%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20whole%20process%20only%20takes%2030%20to%2045%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20industries%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20has%20also%20made%20forays%20into%20the%20residential%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20continuous%20expertise%20for%20regular%20operations%20as%20well%20as%20guidance%20on%20the%20needed%20retrofits%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20their%20STP%20completely%20streamlined%20and