ani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mansi%20Jain%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMansi%20Jain%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPan-India%20presence%20and%20funding%20their%20ambition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20currently%20operational%20in%20about%2014%20states%20and%20has%20raised%20about%20%241.2%20million%20from%20global%20investors%20like%20Elemental%20Excelerator%20and%20Echo%20River%20Capital%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%20investors%20like%20Enzia%2C%20Peer%20Cheque%2C%20SAE%2C%20DevC%2C%20Bharat%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20and%20leading%20angels%20like%20Ashish%20Goel%20(Urban%20Ladder)%2C%20Yamini%20Bhatt%20(Wymo)%20and%20Mohit%20Tandon%20(Delhivery).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Karuna%20Jain%20and%20Shivam%20Jindal%20of%20Enzia%20Ventures%2C%20a%20venture%20capital%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enzia.vc%2Fperspective-posts%2Fwhy-we-invested-in-digital-paani%5C%