ive%20buildings%20and%20industries%20that%20in%20turn%20significantly%20improve%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20our%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalpaani.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20Paani%3C%2Fa%3E%2FInstagram%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fdigital-paani-making-watertech-work-alexander-hogeveen-rutter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%2FAlexander%20Hogeveen%20Rutter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBharatFounders%2Fstatus%2F1775471473580286296%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%2FBharat%20Founders%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718116327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mansi%20Jain%2C%20a%20graduate%20of%20environmental%20economics%20from%20Stanford%20University%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20Jain%2C%20a%20product%20of%20IIT-Delhi%2C%20founded%20their%20startup%20Digital%20Paani%20to%20help%20industries%20and%20residential%20societies%20treat%20their%20wastewater%20more%20efficiently%20and%20at%20a%20lower%20cost.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20This%20Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Patented%20Grow%20Bags%2C%20You%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Need%20to%20Worry%20About%20Watering%20Your%20Plants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lush%20landscapes%20of%20Malabar%2C%20amidst%20sprawling%20coffee%2C%20cocoa%2C%20and%20rubber%20plantations%2C%20Eyyo%20Kuriakose%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20farming%20blossomed.%20Growing%20up%2C%20he%20spent%20countless%20hours%20assisting%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%20on%20their%20farm%2C%20an%20experience%20that%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20a%20lifetime%20commitment%20to%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20at%2078%2C%20Eyyo%20has%20witnessed%20significant%20shifts%20in%20farming%20practices%2C%20driven%20by%20alarming%20changes%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331849%2Fgardening-dr-navdeep-singh-khurana-dentist-amritsar-flowers-vegetables-indoor-garden%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20increased%20pest%20attacks%2C%20which%20have%20impacted%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20observation%20kindled%20in%20Eyyo%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20pushing%20him%20to%20explore%20sustainable%20and%20healthier%20methods%20of%20crop%20cultivation.%20Unlike%20conventional%20practices%20that%20often%20rely%20heavily%20on%20chemical%20inputs%2C%20organic%20farming%20presents%20a%20harmonious%20alternative%2C%20promising%20a%20return%20to%20eco-friendly%20practices%20without%20sacrificing%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%E2%80%99s%20approach%20was%20always%20to%20stay%20abreast%20with%20the%20latest%20agricultural%20innovations%2C%20adapting%20and%20implementing%20new%20methods%20that%20could%20support%20the%20environment%20and%20yield%20healthy%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Kottayam%20resident%20made%20the%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming%20after%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20avoid%20inorganic%20vegetables%20commonly%20available%20in%20markets.%20Starting%20with%20basic%20gardening%20using%20standard%20grow%20bags%2C%20he%20soon%20discovered%20the%20limitations%20of%20these%20products%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20prone%20to