he%20impact%20of%20these%20durable%20grow%20bags%20could%20be%20significant%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agriculture%20practices.%20By%20reducing%20water%20usage%20and%20enhancing%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20grow%20materials%2C%20these%20bags%20represent%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20solving%20some%20of%20the%20persistent%20challenges%20in%20vegetable%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20organic%20journey%20leading%20to%20a%20patented%20grow%20bag%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%20was%20first%20introduced%20to%20organic%20farming%20while%20still%20in%20Malabar%2C%20where%20he%20experimented%20with%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20determine%20what%20worked%20best%20for%20various%20crops.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20he%20expanded%20his%20organic%20farming%20practices%20to%20include%20livestock.%20On%20his%20three-acre%20farm%2C%20cows%20and%20goats%20coexist%20with%20vegetables.%20He%20notes%20that%20cow%20dung%20serves%20as%20an%20excellent%20fertiliser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20consuming%20the%20vegetables%20that%20were%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Reading%20about%20the%20ill%20effects%20of%20consuming%20food%20with%20pesticides%20prompted%20me%20to%20start%20growing%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eyyo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296470%2Faward-winning-kerala-terrace-farmer-grows-seasonal-veggies-zucchini-cauliflower%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20typically%20used%20for%20indoor%20farming%2C%20the%20septuagenarian%20decided%20to%20try%20them%20outdoors.%20His%20initial%20experiments%20with%20traditional%20plastic%20grow%20bags%20were%20unsatisfactory.%20Concurrently%2C%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20rampant%20disposal%20of%20plastic%20bottles.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20wonder%20%E2%80%94%20could%20a%20plastic%20bottle%20be%20used%20to%20water%20his%20plants%20slowly%2C%20mimicking%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system%3F%20The%20answer%20he%20discovered%20was%20a%20resounding%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20initially%20began%20by%20modifying%20traditional%20plastic%20grow%20bags%2C%20making%20holes%20to%20add%20water.%20However%2C%20these%20bags%20didn%E2%80%99t%20last%20long.%20After%20months%20of%20trials%2C%20he%20found%20his%20solution%20in%20silpaulin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20durable%2C%20waterproof%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eyyo%20with%20his%20patented%20grow%20bag%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-3-min-1718113042-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352693%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEyyo%20with%20his%20patented%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20the%20bag%20to%20thrive%20in%20all%20weather%20conditions%20while%20keeping%20pests%20at%20bay.%20Grow%20bags%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20methods%20to%20grow%20vegetables%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20even%20better.%20I%20designed%20the%20bag%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20needs%20less%20water%20and%20provides%20a%20good%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Eyyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rectangular%20grow%20bag%20features%20two%20large%20holes%20on%20the%20top%20for%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20smaller%20holes%20on%20the%20bottom%20and%20sides%20for%20excess%20water%20drainage.%20It%20is%20spacious%20enough%20to%20allow%20plants%20to%20grow%20freely.%20To%20use%20it%2C%20you%20fill%20a%20water%20bottle%2C%20turn%20it%20upside%20down%2C%20and%20quickly%20place%20it%20in%20the%20hole%20to%20prevent%20leakage.%20The%20farmer%20advises%20ensuring%20no%20air%20enters%20the%20bottle%20while%20pressing%20it%20into%20the%20soil.%20This%20method%20ensures%20that%20water%20is%20directed%20precisely%20to%20the%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20reduces%20water%20wastage%20and%20secures%20a%20consistent%20supply%20of%20moisture%20to%20the%20plant%20roots.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20leave%20the%20bottle%20after%20inserting.%20The%20water%20will%20slowly%20percolate%20as%20per%20the%20requirement.%20I%20generally%20use%20a%20one-litre%20bottle%2C%20which%20suffices%20for%20at%20least%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Eyyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20provides%20an%20optimum%20use%20of%20plastic%20water%20bottles.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20many%20use%20this%20method%2C%20we%20can%20prevent%20many%20plastic%20bottles%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%20prepares%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288760%2Fhow-to-grow-organic-ginger-in-grow-bags-and-sacks-kerala-farmer-shares-steps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20mix%20for%20his%20grow%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20starts%20by%20ploughing%20some%20topsoil%20and%20mixing%20in%20some%20lime%20powder%20(%3Cem%3Ekummayam%3C%2Fem%3E).%20He%20then%20leaves%20this%20mixture%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20for%2010%20days%2C%20regularly%20sprinkling%20water%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20prepares%20another%20mixture%20using%20powdered%20cow%20dung%2C%20powdered%20bone%20meal%20(%3Cem%3Eellupodi%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20neem%20press%20cake%20(%3Cem%3Evep%20pinnakku%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20groundnut%20cake%20(%3Cem%3Ekadala%20pinnakku%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20trichoderma%2C%20and%20super%20phosphate%20or%20mussoorie%20phos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mixture%20is%20stirred%20daily%20for%20six%20to%20seven%20days%2C%20with%20water%20added%20periodically.%20Finally%2C%20the%20two%20mixtures%20are%20combined%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grow%20bag%20is%20designed%20so%20that%20the%20mixture%20does%20not%20come%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20soil%20beneath%2C%20effectively%20preventing%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%20from%20spreading.%20Eyyo%20shares%20that%20this%20grow%20bag%20is%20patented%20and%20much%20more%20durable%20than%20standard%20ones%2C%20lasting%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20potentially%20even%20longer%20when%20used%20in%20home%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20bag%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20461px)%20100vw%2C%20461px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%20461w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-150x333.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692.jpeg%20576w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%2