k%20you%20to%20propose%20a%20glass%20of%20water.%20Many%20YouTube%20Shorts%20go%20viral%20but%20such%20irrelevant%20questions%20are%20never%20asked%20in%20real%20interviews.%20Some%20people%20and%20institutes%20are%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20the%20system.%20But%20mock%20interviews%20are%20nowhere%20close%20to%20real%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20IAS%20Aaditya%20Pandey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20interviewer%20panel%20comprises%20five%20experts%20in%20their%2050s%20and%2060s.%20They%20have%20a%20combined%20experience%20of%20five%20times%20our%20ages.%20Except%20for%20a%20few%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20several%20others%20make%20a%20fool%20out%20of%20aspirants%2C%20like%20asking%20them%20to%20propose%20a%20glass%20of%20water%20and%20what%20to%20do%20if%20this%20was%20their%20last%20day%20of%20life.%20Do%20not%20blindly%20rely%20on%20such%20videos.%20It%20cannot%20compete%20with%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20clearing%20Prelims%20and%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20are%20required%20to%20go%20through%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20UPSC%20(Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20the%20interview%20round.%20The%20goal%20of%20the%20interview%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281857%2Fupsc-cse-interview-topper-ias-apala-mishra-score-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%20test%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20to%20evaluate%20their%20aptitude%2C%20ability%20to%20interact%20with%20people%2C%20and%20interest%20in%20current%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Aaditya%2C%20who%20secured%20190%20marks%20in%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20interview%2C%20and%20spare%20candidates%20from%20falling%20into%20the%20trap%20of%20mock%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20si