3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAaditya%20says%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-fill-detailed-application-form-daf-ias-irs-ifs-officers-share-tips-aspirants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDetailed%20Application%20Form%20%3C%2Fa%3E(DAF)%20is%20very%20crucial%20for%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20Mains%2C%20candidates%20need%20to%20fill%20out%20DAF%20which%20contains%20details%20like%20hometown%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20interests.%20Do%20not%20fill%20them%20recklessly%20as%20initial%20questions%20can%20be%20framed%20from%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInterviews%20are%20very%20subjective.%20The%20first%20question%20asked%20in%20the%20interview%20determines%20the%20interview%20flow%20and%20whether%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20mould%20it%20in%20your%20favour.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20command%20of%20your%20DAF%2C%20then%20you%20will%20be%20able%20to%20sail%20through%20the%20interview%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20DAF%2C%20Aaditya%20mentioned%20listening%20to%20Ramcharitmanas%20(an%20epic%20poem%20that%20contains%20the%20deeds%20of%20Lord%20Rama)%20and%20watching%20Korean%20dramas%20as%20his%20interests.%20This%20framed%20his%20interview%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20similarities%20and%20differences%20between%20ancient%20values%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Indian%20and%20Korean%20societies.%20Another%20question%20was%20based%20on%20the%20division%20of%20Korea%20and%20its%20war%20history.%20Later%20on%2C%20we%20spoke%20on%20the%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20which%20I%20did%20not%20mention%20in%20my%20DAF%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c