s%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20scepticism%20was%20also%20rooted%20in%20the%20belief%20that%20only%20large%20properties%2C%20like%20the%20grand%20%3Cem%3Ehavelis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Jaipur%20with%2050%20or%20100%20rooms%2C%20could%20attract%20guests.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20intimate%20setting%20would%20work%20just%20as%20well.%20After%20persistent%20persuasion%2C%20my%20father%20finally%20agreed%20during%20Diwali%20in%202017%2C%20offering%20to%20finance%20the%20project%20while%20leaving%20the%20execution%20up%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20several%20years%2C%20they%20remained%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20project%2C%20networking%20with%20individuals%20in%20the%20travel%20industry%20and%20inviting%20experts%20to%20provide%20feedback.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestoration%20process%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20in%202019%2C%20we%20proudly%20opened%20our%20homestay%2C%20blending%20our%20rich%20heritage%20with%20modern%20hospitality%2C%20allowing%20visitors%20to%20experience%20the%20charm%20and%20history%20of%20our%20ancestral%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20restoration%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20maintain%20the%20original%20structure%20while%20enhancing%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20which%20was%20previously%20unused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20family%20continued%20living%20on%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20keeping%20our%20personal%20and%20guest%20spaces%20separate.%20The%20restoration%20aimed%20to%20preserve%20the%20original%20architecture%2C%20using%20local%20artisans%20without%20involving%20any%20architects%2C%20engineers%2C%20or%20designers%20due%20to%20the%20small%20and%20remote%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2