C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20haveli%20was%20restored%20keeping%20intact%20the%20original%20structure%20and%20design.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-13-1717768264-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352427%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20haveli%20was%20restored%20keeping%20intact%20the%20original%20structure%20and%20design.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConverting%20our%20ancestral%20home%20into%20a%20hotel%20in%202019%20was%20a%20significant%20step%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20share%20our%20rich%20history%20and%20heritage%20with%20visitors%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20can%20you%20do%20at%20the%20haveli%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuests%20visiting%20the%20homestay%20can%20indulge%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20activities%2C%20primarily%20focused%20on%20leopard%20safaris%20and%20nature%20experiences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20customised%20jeep%20safaris%2C%20ensuring%20a%20unique%20and%20immersive%20adventure.%20Upon%20checking%20in%2C%20guests%20have%20the%20option%20to%20enjoy%20lunch%20at%20the%20homestay%20or%20take%20a%20packed%20meal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20afternoon%2C%20we%20embark%20on%20the%20safari%2C%20bringing%20along%20a%20delightful%20high%20tea%20setup%2C%20complete%20with%20homemade%20tea%2C%20coffee%2C%20cookies%2C%20and%20other%20treats.%20We%20set%20up%20near%20Jawai%20Lake%2C%20a%20man-made%20lake%20constructed%20by%20the%20Maharaja%20of%20Jodhpur%20in%201952%20for%20drinking%20and%20agricultural%20purposes.%20As%20the%20sun%20sets%2C%20we%20venture%20out%20in%20search%20of%20leopards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20safari%2C%20guests%20can%20relax%20with%20drinks%20and%20enjoy%20a%20campfire%2C%20sharing%20stories%20with%20fellow%20travellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20dinner%2C%20we%20offer%20a%20unique%20dining%20experience%20in%20a%20restored%20old%20stable%2C%20creating%20an%20authentic%20and%20cosy%20atmosphere.%20Our%20meals%20feature%20regional%20and%20seasonal%20dishes%2C%20prepared%20using%20200-year-old%20family%20recipes.%20We%20source%20almost%20all%20ingredients%20locally%2C%20ensuring%20fresh%20and%20authentic%20flavours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20guests%20stay%20for%20multiple%20nights%20and%20are%20interested%20in%20bird%20watching%2C%20they%20organise%20bird-watching%20tours%20around%20the%20lake%20and%20nearby%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20mornings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Armed%20with%20high-quality%20binoculars%20and%20cameras%2C%20guests%20can%20spot%20and%20identify%20various%20bird%20species%20from%20our%20comprehensive%20booklet%2C%20which%20features%20over%20100%20birds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Ffeature-photos-14-1717768365.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bhanwar%20Paramveer%20Singh%20Deora%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20Bhanwar%20Veer%20Vinod%20Singh%20co-founders%20of%20the%20homestay.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F