confidence%20to%20actually%20build%20materials%20that%20can%20replace%20plastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20spent%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Khushboo%20formally%20launched%20her%20company%20in%202021%20along%20with%20her%20brother%20Ronak%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Chanakya%20Medh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInk%20from%20seaweed%2C%20bubble%20wrap%20from%20coir%20%26amp%3B%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShedding%20light%20on%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20packaging%20industry%2C%20Khushboo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20multiple%20types%20of%20plastic%20used%20for%20different%20applications.%20For%20example%2C%20ink%20printed%20on%20the%20packaging%20is%20toxic%20as%20well%2C%20and%20contains%20heavy%20metal%20additives%2C%20synthetic%20chemicals%2C%20and%20paraffin%20waxes.%20So%20even%20if%20you%20have%20a%20compostable%20material%2C%20you%20have%20to%20print%20on%20it%C2%A0%20with%20regular%2C%20toxic%20ink.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSimilarly%2C%20people%20fail%20to%20notice%20layers%20of%20plastic%20lamination%20on%20packaging%20and%20the%20synthetic%20glue%20used%20in%20the%20sticker%20industry.%20These%20are%20the%20areas%20we%20strived%20to%20work%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20material%20innovation%20company%2C%20Khushboo%E2%80%99s%20aim%20was%20to%20solve%20industrial%20problems%20using%20natural%20materials%20which%20can%20be%20composted%20at%20home.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20innovated%20a%20coating%20compostable%20at%20home%20which%20naturally%20makes%20paper%20water-resistant%20and%20heat-fillable%20%E2%80%94%20two%20main%20properties%20that%20plastic%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgo-do-good-st