9CThese%20materials%20allow%20everything%20that%20is%20on%20the%20package%20and%20inside%20the%20package%20to%20be%20100%20percent%20biodegradable.%20and%20compostable%20at%20home.%20So%2C%20tomorrow%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20done%20using%20the%20product%2C%20you%20can%20dump%20it%20in%20your%20backyard%20and%20it%20will%20compost%20within%2030%20to%2045%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Khushoo%20says%2C%20the%20price%20difference%20is%20also%20at%20par%20with%20only%20a%2010%20percent%20difference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20market%2C%20a%20250g%20paper%20pillow%20pouch%20with%20a%20plastic%20lamination%20(the%20pouches%20in%20which%20items%20like%20milk%2C%20chips%2C%20spices%20are%20sold%20in)%20costs%20Rs%207%20whereas%20our%20natural%20pouch%20costs%20between%20Rs%207.5%20to%208.%20We%20made%20our%20products%20affordable%20and%20compatible%20so%20that%20it%20would%20be%20easier%20for%20more%20and%20more%20people%20to%20switch%20to%20natural%20materials%20instead%20of%20plastic%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khushboo's%20startup%20has%20innovated%20eco-friendly%20coating%20which%20replaces%20the%20laminated%20paper.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-1717688331-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-me